programme.title: Dave Brubeck and Paul Desmond live in Belgium
programme.desc: Dave Brubeck: Live in 64 boasts a beautifully filmed concert from one of the most beloved quartets in jazz history. Captured at the pinnacle of their power and popularity, Paul Desmond (alto sax), Joe Morello (drums), Eugene Wright (bass) and Dave Brubeck (piano) explore the trails they blazed into the realm of odd time signatures with "Forty Days" and two versions of their groundbreaking hit Take Five, as well as forays into world music with a unique interpretation of Koto Song. Their intimate onstage chemistry and impeccable musicianship made the DBQ an award-winning jazz supergroup.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: WOMEX 2018
programme.desc: Since 1994, World Music Expo (WOMEX) has been attracting musicians, agents, a great number of press agencies, as well as media companies from all over the world. Its main exposition event has been held in various locations throughout Europe, including Berlin, Brussels, Marseille, Stockholm, Seville, Cardiff, and Budapest. In 2018, WOMEX was held in Las Palmas, Gran Canaria.

programme.title: La nuit des gitans
programme.desc: The Royal Conservatoire of Liège hosted a "Night of the Gypsies" at the International Guitar Festival of Liège in 1995. At this occasion, the Raphaël Faÿs Trio and Quintet paid tribute to Romani-Belgian jazz guitarist Django Reinhardt. Raphaël Faÿs (solo guitar), Pierre Blanchard (violin), Daniel Manzanas (guitar), Pablo Gilabert (bass) and Miguel Sanchez (percussion) play Reinhardts greatest gypsy jazz hits, including It Had To Be You, How High The Moon, Sweet Georgia Brown, and Minor Swing. Enjoy Raphaël Faÿss fresh take on the light-fingered string sound and swinging rhythms of Django Reinhardts gypsy jazz!

programme.title: North Sea Jazz Classics
programme.desc: Registration of the performance of the Ahmad Jamal Trio at North Sea Jazz on July 16.

programme.title: Belgium Sessions
programme.desc: DJAZZ Belguim Sessions shows us some of the best jazz musicians in Europe whom give us a glimpse into their creative process where young talented and established names are mentioned at the AED studios in lint, Belguim.

programme.title: Louis "Satchmo" Armstrong and His All Stars
programme.desc: Louis Armstrong: Live in 59 is one of the only known complete Armstrong concerts from the 1950s to be captured on film. This 55-minute set, filmed in Belgium in 1959, features many of Satchmos greatest songs including Mack The Knife, When Its Sleepy Time Down South and "Stompin" At The Savoy, backed by his stellar band the All-Stars, featuring Trummy Young, Peanuts Hucko, Billy Kyle, Danny Barcelona and Mort Herbert.

programme.title: Piano and Sax
programme.sub-title: Piano and Sax: Charlie Mariano and Wolfgang Dauner
programme.desc: Piano and saxophone - this is an individualistic jazz duo combination. But the melodiousness and maturity of Charlie Marianos saxophone and the freshness and feistiness of Wolfgang Dauners piano turn the meeting of these two jazz greats into a thrilling interplay.

programme.title: Seine Sessions
programme.desc: Jam session dates brought back to the 1920s, when white and black musicians sought out a smoky bar after their paid performances to play the jazz they didnt get the chance to do in their Paul Whiteman style bands.

programme.title: The Morgenland Festival
programme.desc: Since 2005, the Morgenland Festival of Osnabrueck has dedicated itself to the fascinating music culture of the Near and Middle East. From traditional and classical music to avant-garde, jazz, and rock, the festival program also features art, such as visual arts, dance, and theatre of interdisciplinary projects. "Viva" is a perfect mixture of various instruments and musicians from all over the world. Vocalists Aynur and Dima Oshno perform with the All Star Band. Aynur sings about the life and sufferings of Kurdish people, in particular Kurdish women. Musically, she tries to blend Kurdish and Western music, creating her own style and interpreting the traditional repertoire in a modern and fresh way.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: Sarah Vaughan Live in 58 and 64
programme.sub-title: Sarah Vaughan Live in 58 and 64: The Divine One
programme.desc: Sarah Vaughan: Live in 58 and 64 features the "Divine One" in her prime, wrapping her sultry voice around jazz standards such as Lover Man, "Misty" and "I Got Rhythm" and soaring on popular showtunes such as "Over The Rainbow" and Maria. One of the greatest voices of the 20th Century, her renditions of songs by Harold Arlen, Leonard Bernstein, Johnny Burke, the Gershwins and Stephen Sondheim are pure diva magic. These three performances demonstrate why Sarah Vaughan is invariably mentioned in the same breath as Ella Fitzgerald and Billie Holiday.

programme.title: Georgie Fame and the Blue Flames
Milt Jacksons Modern Jazz Quartet at the Bozar
programme.desc: The Modern Jazz Quartet (MJQ) was composed of Milt "Bags" Jackson on vibraphone, John Lewis on piano, Percy Heath on bass, and Connie Kay on drums. Milt Jackson and John Lewis were pioneer bebop musicians who had played together in Dizzy Gillespies 1948 big band. They pursued separate careers before adding Heath and Lewis to form the Modern Jazz Quartet in the 1950s. Noted for its delicate percussion sonorities, innovative jazz forms, and high performance standards, the MJQ was an immensely popular jazz and "third stream" ensemble until its final concerts in the early 1990s.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: La Mambanegra - Music Meeting Festival 2018
programme.desc: The latin music orchestra, La Mambanegra, combines many musical elements, such as Jamaican or Colombian music, as well as Funk and Hip Hop. Yet, their main musical influence comes from 1970s New York, where during the time Salsa was born. The magic of the genre, however, is given new colours by La Mambanegra: with a series of fantastic adventures in Cali, La Habana and New York, the bands music is inspired by an anonymous and even mythical hero of the Calis popular neighborhood Barrio Obrero. Consisting of 8 talented musicians, La Mambanegra presents their charming showcase at the Music Meeting Festival in Nijmegen, The Netherlands.

programme.title: Michelle David - Jazz in Duketown
programme.desc: Jazz in Duketown is the largest free outdoor jazz festival in the Netherlands. Its a real gathering for jazz addicts, inviting internationall renowned artists. The talented American singer Michelle David performs pop and gospel music that feeds the heart and soothes the soul. Having grown up with the church, she started singing at the age of four. A year later she joined her first band, The Mission of Love. In 1980 she enrolled at Fiorello H. LaGuardia High School of Music and Art and Performing Arts in New York City, known from the film Fame. During this time, she appeared as an extra in the legendary comedy film Ghostbusters. Musicals and tours with the bands of Diana Ross and Michael Bolton followed.

programme.title: Duets
programme.sub-title: Duets: Carla Bley and Steve Swallow in 1988
programme.desc: If any two musicians share a special bond when they perform, its pianist Carla Bley and bassist Steve Swallow. The two have performed in the same bands since the 1960s and have been romantic partners for more than two decades. Watching them perform is the definition of musical telepathy. A glance or a smile seems to change the feel of the music. In 1988, Swallow and Bley began performing duet concerts in Europe, United States, South America and Japan. This performance of Duets, their album of songs arranged for piano and bass, was released that same year. The performance showcases their approach to traditional jazz, folk and classical music, as well as their poignant musical story.

programme.title: Rebirth
programme.desc: Amsterdam, February 6th, 2018 - The short documentary Rebirth in The Amsterdam Red Light District illustrates how brutal Richard Lems life as an addict was and his struggle to unshackle himself from the shame. Filled with fierce, freighting, and sad moments, Richard relives his stabbing, stay in jail, drug test, and drug use. Richard expresses himself verbally but mainly relives the moments through drumming, which renders the documentary an intense and unique experience. Addiction doctor and musician Gerard Alderliefste: "If he dares to bottom out, he will see it was the drugs and not himself. Music can bring those emotions to the surface".

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: Jim Hall and Atilla Zoller - Extensions
programme.desc: This selection of unforgettable performances by some of the most iconic and influential jazz guitarists in history showcases these legends unique essence. Revel in Wes Montgomerys virtuosity as he performs the captivating "Nicas Dream" in Holland in 1965, and delight in the expressive beauty of his rendition of "Heres That Rainy Day", recorded in London in that same year. Experience the timeless appeal of Joe Passs "You Stepped Out of a Dream" and "You Turned The Tables on Me", recorded live in Hanover in 1975. The interplay between Jim Hall and Atilla Zoller borders on the impossible as they perform "Extensions" in Hanover in 1973. Enjoy Jim Halls lyrical solo performance of "Im Getting Sentimental Over You" from 1964. Witness Sonny Sharrocks avant-garde fusion of jazz and rock in an exhilarating performance of "Peanut", recorded live in France in 1970. Sharrock is joined by flutist Herbie Mann in a soulful performance of "Memphis Underground" from 1969. Immerse yourself in the magic of jazz guitar!

programme.title: Paradox Live
programme.sub-title: Paradox Live: Bertus Borgers and The Young Retros
programme.desc: Innovative contemporary jazz and improvised music, the search for modernity, mind blowing sounds, rock and pop… Indeed PARADOX Tilburg goes beyond jazz, crossing musical boundaries into the unknown soundscapes of electronic music. Indie artists, blues veterans and jazz superstars all pour their hearts and souls at the Paradox. From young, local talents to top national and international artists, PARADOX Tilburg is the most intimate jazz club in the Netherlands, with a devoted audience from all across Europe. In their TV show PARADOX LIVE you get a taste of the greatest concerts and interviews with artists from all around the world. This episode of PARADOX LIVE presents the Tilburg based Bertus Borgers and his Young Retros!

programme.title: Wynton in the South Bank Show
programme.desc: Considered one of the most technically brilliant players in the history of the trumpet, jazz musician Wynton Marsalis is also a master of classical music and a fine composer. Marsalis takes the cameras with him around New York, to his home town of New Orleans, and to his rehearsal studios where he and his assembled band of musicians are seen putting together the album Blood on the Fields. He also talks about his music and his way of working.

programme.title: PC Qwintett
programme.desc: Pierre Courbois has been one of Europes leading jazz musicians since the mid-sixties. This concert, recorded at the renowned Amsterdam jazz club Bimhuis, sees the drummer playing with his QWINTETT. On the occasion of his 75th birthday in 2015, Courbois hit the road for the Pierre Courbois 75 Years Anniversary Tour. The PC QWINTETT consists of several highly acclaimed Dutch jazz musicians with whom Courbois has worked before in his long and versatile career. Among them are pianist Nike Langenhuijsen, double bassist Egon Kracht, trumpeter Toon de Gouw, and trombonist Ilja Reijngoud. QWINTETT honours the Charles Mingus tradition of thematic and melodic ensemble jazz - but also with an unmistakable Courbois groove! Courbois, known for his own way of combining compositions with improvisations, melodically melts constructions with uneven breaks.

programme.title: B.B. King
programme.sub-title: B.B. King: The King of the Blues in Stuttgart
programme.desc: This uptempo, funky performance proves that B.B. King, one of the Masters of the Blues Guitar has still got it. The band features some of todays best blues musicians playing all of B.B. Kings classic songs.

programme.title: WOMEX 2018
programme.desc: Since 1994, World Music Expo (WOMEX) has been attracting musicians, agents, a great number of press agencies, as well as media companies from all over the world. Its main exposition event has been held in various locations throughout Europe, including Berlin, Brussels, Marseille, Stockholm, Seville, Cardiff, and Budapest. In 2018, WOMEX was held in Las Palmas, Gran Canaria.

programme.title: Sammy Price and the Harlem Beggars
programme.desc: Pianist, singer and civil rights activist Sammy Price is joined by the gospel singers known as the Harlem Beggars for spirited renditions of "Go Tell It on the Mountain," "Im a Soldier," and "When the Saints Go Marching In," among several others. The group is joined by Wilbert Harrison, who provides accompaniment on organ.

programme.title: The MotorMusic Jazz Sessions
programme.desc: In this unique series,The MotorMusic Studios in Mechelen, Belgium, exert a magnetic attraction on countless first class jazz musicians. Where many of them visit international jazz musicians who share their views of their music with us.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: Marion Williams Sings Spirituals
programme.desc: You cant help but be carried away by the powerful voice Marion Williams, who, with backing from Tommy Brown (piano), Joe Washington (organ), Billy Tuliver (drums), and singers Barbara White and Ann Bolden, sings gospel songs and spirituals as if she has lived them a thousand times over. The repertoire includes such familiar tunes as "Peace in the Valley," "We Shall Overcome," and "Michael, Row the Boat Ashore."

programme.title: Aki Rissanen Trio at Jazzclub Unterfahrt, Munich
programme.desc: Aki Rissanens interest in jazz came after he started taking classical piano lessons. His deep interest in improvised music placed him among top jazz pianist in his home country - Finland. While composing and performing his own music, Rissanen has also collaborated with Verneri Pohjola and Dave Liebman, and today his name appears among the top European jazz musicians. Live from "Jazzclub Unterfahrt" in Munich, Germany, together with Antti Lotjonen on bass and Teppo Makynen on drums, Rissanen showcases the best of Scandinavian jazz and its DNA - the Nordic Tone.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: Jazzwoche Burghausen
programme.desc: Every year since 1970, the German city of Burghausen has been hosting one of the largest jazz festivals in the world. During Burghausen International Jazz Week, Burghausen becomes a Bavarian jazz mecca: guests from all over the world join the Burghausers to enjoy the most wonderful jazz performances as the colorful hustle and bustle of spectators and musicians shake up the city. One of the bands performing here in 2019 is the Hypnotic Brass Ensemble, which consists of eight sons of jazz trumpeter and one-time Sun Ra Arkestra member Phil Cohran. He trained his children to play their horns and instilled in them a profound sense of the deeply spiritual roots of the music. The Hypnotic Brass Ensembles music ranges from hypnotizing grooves to jazzy funk.

programme.title: Sven Hammond Soul
programme.sub-title: Sven Hammond Soul: Tivoli de Helling
programme.desc: Although its music might sound like the sound track of any 1970s American car chase movie, the band Sven Hammond Soul is from the Netherlands. This steaming soul machine is headed by Sven Figee, who prefers to attack rather than play his Hammond organ. In April 2012, the band was augmented with vocalist Jenny Lane. Todays recordings were made at a steaming live performance at Utrechts Tivoli in 2012.

programme.title: North Sea Jazz Classics
programme.desc: Registration of the performance of the Ahmad Jamal Trio at North Sea Jazz on July 16.

programme.title: Count Basie and his Orchestra live in Charleroi
programme.desc: Count Basie is one of the most important bandleaders of the swing era. With the exception of a brief period in the early 50s, he led a big band from 1935 until his death almost 50 years later. Basies orchestra was characterized by a light, swinging rhythm section that he led from the piano, lively ensemble work, and generous soloing. Basie was not a composer like Duke Ellington or an important soloist like Benny Goodman. His instrument was his band, which was considered the epitome of swing and deeply influenced jazz. In this 1961 concert recording, Count Basie takes the stage in Charleroi.

programme.title: Kurhaus Scheveningen
programme.desc: The Dutch world-class jazz pianist Peter Beets has shared the stage with jazz greats like Chick Corea, Wynton Marsalis, "Toots" Thielemans, Elvin Jones, George Coleman, Johnny Griffin, Benny Golson and John Clayton. From birth, Beets was surrounded by music: he heard classical music from his mother, who is a music pedagogue, and he heard jazz from his father, who has a great fan of Oscar Peterson and Art Blakey. Although Beets parents originally did not associate the word "musician" with the word "career", music is definitely in the familys blood. At this concert at the Kurhaus in Scheveningen, the Netherlands, Peter Beets teams up with the world-famous guitarist Kurt Rosenwinkel. With a career spanning almost twenty-five years and including collaborating with dynamic peers like Brad Mehldau, Brian Blade, Mark Turner, Joshua Redman, Chris Potter, as well as esteemed jazz legends like Joe Henderson, Paul Motian and Gary Burton, Rosenwinkels indelible mark in music is the consummation of being steeped in the rich and deep traditions of jazz, springing off of the shoulders of such vital underpinnings to elevate his own art to new heights, evolving the language in a way no other guitarist has since his arrival. This collaboration between Beets and Rosenwinkel guarantees brilliant music.

programme.title: Anita Oday Live in Sweden 1963
programme.desc: Anita ODay boasts two wonderful concerts from 1963 and 1970 that present the "jazz singer supreme" in impeccable form. ODays horn-based approach to singing is in full effect throughout both shows including stand-out renditions in each show of audience favorites "Tea For Two" and "Sweet Georgia Brown" (both reprised from her triumphant appearance at the 1958 Newport Jazz Festival.) This show is a fitting testimony to one of jazz musics true originals and shows unequivocally why she is ranked in the top tier of vocalists along with Ella Fitzgerald, Sarah Vaughan, and Billie Holiday.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips

programme.title: Lex Jasper Trio
programme.sub-title: Lex Jasper Trio: Happy Days Are Here Again
programme.desc: Lex Jasper Trio: Happy Days Are Here Again - the title says is all… After an automobile accident and 15 years of revalidation, he is back! Together with his musical pals Edwin Corzilius (double bass) and Frits Landesbergen (drums), pianist and composer Lex Jasper celebrates his return to jazz club The Duke in the Dutch village of Nistelrode. Following his car accident, Lex nearly joined the leagues of Netherlands "forgotten" jazz heroes, though he is still considered one of the most important artists and composers of his generation and Dutch jazz history. Jasper played and recorded with all the greats, including Toots Thielemans, Clark Terry, Joe Pass, and Rita Reys.

programme.title: Les McCann
programme.sub-title: Les McCann: Live in New Orleans
programme.desc: Autodidact Les McCann became an international jazz star he is today after the release of his album "Swiss Movement" in 1968 which was recorded with Eddie Harris. However this musician has many other sides of achievements than that one record such as; McCann effortlessly switched between styles and stood his ground in every role from bop to fusion, from vocals to electric piano and clavinet to synthesizer, his is mix of church music and swing fits perfectly in the spirit of his time although at one point within the 90s he was only able to play with a single finger due to his illness. In todays broadcast, McCann brings gospel back to the New Orleans where this set was played in 1983. McCanns vocals triumph in the soulful performance of many of his hits, including Just Like Magic. He is accompanied by his fantastic "Magic Band" consisting of saxophonist Bobby Bryant Jr., bassist Curtis Roberson Jr. and drummer Tony St. James.

programme.title: John Coltrane
programme.desc: The mere mention of the name John Coltrane evokes a deeply emotional, often spiritual response from even the most casual jazz fan. Dexter Gordon was a fantastic saxophonist. Miles Davis was a genius. Coltrane stood above - he was a visionary, a saint-like figure. By the standards of most jazz musicians, his life was uneventful. Sure, he had a heroin habit for a while, and Miles Davis punched him, but once hed experienced the "spiritual awakening" described in the liner notes of his 1965 album A Love Supreme, he dedicated himself to his music with extreme single-mindedness. This broadcast of Coltranes 1965 performance at the short-lived Belgian jazz festival in Comblain-la-Tour features Tranes classic quartet with Elvin Jones (drums), Jimmy Garrison (bass) and McCoy Tyner (piano).

programme.title: Jazz in Comblain-la-Tour, 1963
programme.desc: In 1963,small town in Belgium named; Comblain-la-Tour hosted an exciting line up of both new and old jazz groups. The British trombonist Charlie Galbraiths All Star Jazz Band performes classic Dixieland jazz. Next up is German singer Knut Kiesewetter who backs up from the Prague Dixieland Band, sings the blues. Perhaps the highlight of this event is the coupling of American alto saxophonist Bud Shank with Dutch pianist Pim Jacobs and his trio, whom play standards and bossa nova and the French clarinetist Marc Laferrière with his New Orleans Stompers combined with more classic Dixieland.

programme.title: Tribute to Django Reinhardt
programme.sub-title: Tribute to Django Reinhardt: Rosenberg meets Beets
programme.desc: Bireli Lagrène is a French jazz guitarist born on September 4, 1966 in a family of gypsy tradition. His brother and his father introduced him from an early age to the repertoire of Django Reinhardt, whose influence is still felt in the style of Lagrène. In this performance, Lagrène pays homage to Django Reinhardt with his son, Babik Reinhardt.

programme.title: Tribute to Monk
programme.desc: Jazz à Vienne is one of the worlds most prestigious jazz festivals. Ever since 1981, it has attracted a mix of jazz legends and exciting newcomers, with many of them playing return engagements. Each year welcomes outstanding international stars to the historical Le Theâtre Antique to impress and inspire their audiences. In 2017, French pianist Laurent de Wilde performed his tribute to jazz icon Thelonious Monk at Jazz à Vienne. Alongside bassist Jerôme Regard and drummer Donald Kontomanou, De Wilde gives a respectful and engaging homage built upon 20 years of study.

programme.title: Comblain-la-Tour Jazz Festival
programme.sub-title: Comblain-la-Tour Jazz Festival: Jimmy McGriff Trio
programme.desc: As one of the best Hammond B3 organ players, Jimmy McGriff (1936-2008) is often lost among great soul-jazz organists from his hometown of Philadelphia. Of the major soul-jazz pioneers, he was the bluesiest and often insisted that he was more of a blues musician than a jazz artist. Regardless, he remained eclectic enough to blur the lines of genres. His sound - deep, down-to-earth grooves drenched in blues and gospel feeling - made him popular with RandB audiences. This 1965 performance is part of the Comblain-la-Tour Jazz Festival.

programme.title: Charles Mingus And Eric Dolphy live in Liège
programme.desc: Charles Mingus gives an exceptional concert in April 1965 with Mingus who has his most celebrated lineup whereas Jaki Byard (pianoist), Dannie Richmond (drummer), Johnny Coles (trumpeter), Clifford Jordan (tenor saxophonist) and the great Eric Dolphy (alto sax, flute and bass clarinet) were playing their recordings within eight days and less than three months beofre Dolphys death!

programme.title: On the Road With Duke Ellington
programme.sub-title: On the Road With Duke Ellington: I
programme.desc: In May 2014, the Conservatory of Amsterdam hosted a unique conference about one of the greatest jazz composers of the 20th century: Duke Ellington. Musicologists and musicians with a special bond with Ellington and his music spoke about his life and music. Among them were David Schiff, author of The Ellington Century, and Harvey Cohen, author of Duke Ellingtons America. Moreover, concerts were played by jazz pianist Matt Cooper, the Calefax Reed Quintet, and the Concert Big Band of the Conservatory of Amsterdam conducted by David Berger. The winner of the Boy Edgar Prize 2013, viola player Oene van Geel, performed his All Ellington Project.

programme.title: Michel Tasky live in Rio
programme.sub-title: Michel Tasky live in Rio: Um Malandro em Paris
programme.desc: With his relaxed and clear voice, Belgian-born vocalist Michel Tasky took his French-Waalse roots to Brazil, where he established himself in the jazz scene. His contemporary style, which blends jazz and French chanson with a whole lot of samba, transports audiences to faraway places.

programme.title: Jazzed Out Swiss
programme.desc: Jazz performances on the Swiss streets. A range of talented musicians step out of the studio to play in various locations in Switzerlands biggest city: Zurich. Featuring the renowned jazz musicians Erik Truffaz and Malcolm Braff.

programme.title: Live at the Metro Theatre
programme.desc: Theatrical show where both Australian brother and sister from the same band sing together as a due in a concert recorded at The Metro Theatre in Sydney.

programme.title: Hall and Oates - Live at Sydney Entertainment Centre
programme.desc: When Daryl Hall and John Oates took to the stage at Sydneys Entertainment Centre as the iconic bass line of "Maneater" began to play, the fans knew they were in for a treat. This duo may have been opening concerts with that irresistibly smooth number for years, but it never seems to lose its magic, and the crowd - an eclectic mix of teens and baby boomers alike - lapped it up. Daryl Hall and John Oates wisely reunited a few years ago after a string of solo projects, and although Oates no longer sports his signature tache, they put on the kind of show that makes it hard to believe they even considered going their separate ways. Earworms like I Cant Go For That, "Out Of Touch" and "Kiss On My List" were surefire reminders that these guys are absolute hit machines, and their catchy synth-soul classics probably deserve to permeate the airwaves as much today as they did decades ago. These Philly crooners still have it in bucket-loads, so this show should have everyone from diehard Daryl Hall and John Oates fans to kids of the 80s groovin along in no time.

programme.title: Moondog and The London Saxophonique
programme.desc: Moondog, a gaunt, mysterious and extravagantly-garbed blind street musician was celebrated among New Yorkers for two decades before gaining acclaim in Europe as an avant-garde composer conducting orchestras before royalty. Artists such as Charlie Parker, Leonard Bernstein, Steve Reich and Philip Glass have called him one of the great musical visionaries of our century. Day in and day out, the man whose real name is Louis T. Hardin, was as taciturn and unchanging a landmark of the midtown Manhattan streetscape as the George M. Cohan statue in Duffy Square. No matter the weather, he invariably dressed in a homemade robe, sandals, a flowing cape, and a horned Viking helmet - the tangible expression of what he referred to as his "Nordic philosophy". For this show, he teams up with renowned saxophone ensemble London Saxophonic for an eccentric performance.

From young, local talents to top national and international artists, PARADOX Tilburg is the most intimate jazz club in the Netherlands, with a devoted audience from all across Europe. programme.title: Gregory Privat - SOLEY
programme.desc: Pianist Gregory Privats 2020 work "Soley" inhabits a hybrid universe in which voice, piano and synthesizer, Caribbean and electronic music, and the classical and jazz trio traditions coexist and mingle. Aided by Chris Jennings on double bass and Tilo Bertholo on drums, Privat makes his debut as a singer, adding a vocal dimension to the instrumental and narrative levels of "Soley", which lends his music an emotional force that is more powerful than ever before.

programme.title: Michel Legrand Orchestra at Spa, 1982
programme.desc: Known outside jazz circles mainly for his film scores, French composer, arranger and pianist Michel Legrand has had a long and storied career in music. Interpreters of his compositions include jazz legends such as Sarah Vaughan, Stan Getz, and Bill Evans, as well as pop stars such as Barbra Streisand and Frank Sinatra. During this 1982 performance in the Belgian town of Spa, Legrand leads his orchestra through a number of original songs, including "The Summer Knows," "What Are You Doing the Rest of Your Life?" and "Les Moulins de mon Cœur." Singing either in English or French, Legrand delivers a spirited performance with plenty of romantic flair that is sure to capture your heart.

programme.title: TorTube
programme.desc: Jazz fans in television land have come to the right place for their dose of first-rate world jazz: TorTube! Jazz club De Tor in Enschede is one of Europes most authentic jazz venues, with an absolutely unique ambiance. Some of the best musicians from Holland and the rest of the world find their way to De Tor to perform for an appreciative audience of jazz fans. In this broadcast of TorTube, the great trumpeter Eric Vloeimans and his associate, pianist Florian Weber, perform a set named "A good conversation" (Een goed gesprek). Great music and a perfect ambiance prove an irresistible combination!

programme.title: Trio Chemirani
programme.desc: The veritable tombak virtuosos of Trio Chemirani, consisting of Chemirani Senior and Juniors, enrapture the Festival de Saintes. The tombak is a Persian percussion instrument, but its rhythms are universal. The Trio Chemiranis music is accessible to all and will certainly resound with each listener. The members of the trio, Djamchid Chemirani (born in Teheran in 1942) and his two sons and pupils Keyvan and Bijan, are living in France. Their concert performances bring them all over the world, as they explore the endless potential of their Persian percussion instruments. The trio finds also inspiration in Mediterranean modal music and jazz. These three musicians, who might well be thought of as poets are in search of a common language that connects several cultures.

programme.title: Da Pá Virada Sessions
programme.desc: The series Da Pá Virada sessions presents the best musicians of contemporary Brazilian jazz, and beyond. Filmed in Sao Paulo, each session offers a unique experience by giving a fresh look into Brazils music scene. The artists for each session are selected in consultation with Stingray DJAZZs music editor.

programme.title: Jazzahead!
programme.desc: Jazzahead! Bremen in Germany, has an international fair, exhibition and festival which brings musicians, bookers, agents, organizers, musicologists and music lovers all together.

programme.desc: Jazzahead! Bremen in Germany, has an international fair, exhibition and festival which brings musicians, bookers, agents, organizers, musicologists and music lovers all together.

programme.title: Festival Vue sur la Relève
programme.sub-title: Festival Vue sur la Relève: SHPIK
programme.desc: Montreals very own jazz group SHPIK offers a bold and impressionistic music, drawing its inspirations from jazz, nature, and film. Evoking the great outdoors, self-discovery, and navigating between the immense and the infinitely small, this first album offers an intricate musical journey that is both energetic and reflective. Consisting of pianist and composer Arnaud Spick-Saucier, bassist Etienne Dextraze, drummer Philippe Lussier-Baillargeon, and saxophonist/flutist Alex Dodier, SHPIK has performed at famous jazz events, including the Montreal International Jazz Festival. Do yourself a favour by not missing this extraordinary breath of fresh air.

programme.title: Song for my father
programme.desc: Legendary jazz pianist Horace Silvers groundbreaking fusion of hard bop, blues, soulful grooves and Cape Verdean influences have left an indelible mark on the world of jazz. At the renowned Umbria Jazz Festival in the picturesque region of Umbria, Italy, Silver is accompanied by a great band of future all-stars: Bob Berg on tenor sax, Tom Harrell on trumpet, Steve Beskrone on bass and Eddie Gladden on drums. During this performance from July 20, 1976, Silvers quintet stretches out on four Silver originals: "Adjustment", "Barbara", "In Pursuit of the 27th Man", and "Song For My Father". Tune in and let Horace Silvers irresistible music mesmerize you!

programme.title: DJAZZ Portrait
programme.desc: DJAZZ Portraits involves artists, concerts and festivals which provide a good picture of the jazz world within 2016s concerts.

programme.title: North Sea Jazz Classics
programme.desc: Registration of the performance of the Ahmad Jamal Trio at North Sea Jazz on July 16.

programme.title: The Tallberg Foundation
programme.sub-title: The Tallberg Foundation: "Jazz for the Planet"
programme.desc: On October 19, 2021, John Patitucci (bass), Marco Pignataro (sax and musical director), and Joe Lovano (sax) showcased inspirational new originals at GBHs Fraser Performance Studio in Boston, MA, accompanied by Terri Lyne Carrington (drums), Nadia Washington (vocals), Chico Pinheiro (guitar), and Anastassiya Petrova (piano). This recording, titled Tallbergs Jazz for the Planet, was made in support of the Tallberg Foundations message and aims to inspire positive climate action. Since 1981, the Tallberg Foundation has been trying to nurture new thinking, in part by looking at societal challenges through the lenses of artists.

programme.title: Marcus Miller
programme.desc: This portrait of Marcus Miller was included during his 2009 Tutu Revisited tour. Here he looks back on his longstanding partnership with Miles Davis. Miller also talks extensively about his composition Tutu, and explains how the legendary album of the same name came round. This film was included in the exhibition "We Want Miles" at the Paris Cite de la Musique.

programme.title: DJAZZ Clips
programme.desc: An extraordinary collection of clips in all jazz genres from the most beautiful concerts and the most special festivals, performed by the finest jazz musicians.

programme.title: Non Stop Travels
programme.sub-title: Non Stop Travels: The Story of Michel Petrucciani
programme.desc: This film portrays Michel Petrucciani s very unique outlook on life, his vitality, boisterous humor and marked comedian talent which triumphes over all physical restrictions. It also shows Michel Petrucciani performing, composing, selecting his very own piano, at a recording session with Stephane Grapelli, Roy Haynes and Georges Mraz, .... and much more.

programme.title: WOMEX 2018
programme.desc: Since 1994, World Music Expo (WOMEX) has been attracting musicians, agents, a great number of press agencies, as well as media companies from all over the world. Its main exposition event has been held in various locations throughout Europe, including Berlin, Brussels, Marseille, Stockholm, Seville, Cardiff, and Budapest. In 2018, WOMEX was held in Las Palmas, Gran Canaria.

programme.title: Duke Ellington live at the Concertgebouw Amsterdam
programme.desc: Duke Ellington: Live in 58 features the earliest-known filmed full-length concert by one of the 20th Centurys greatest songwriters and bandleaders. Filmed at Amsterdams famed Concertgebouw, this 80-minute concert features the 16-piece Duke Ellington Orchestra two years after their stunning performance at the 1956 Newport Jazz Festival, which Duke considered his second birth. This epic performance includes legendary players Clark Terry, Johnny Hodges, Harry Carney, Paul Gonsalves, Quentin Jackson and Ray Nance performing some of the most beloved American music ever written.

programme.title: Inga Lindstrom

Emilia kohtab aga endises kodupaigas Morgonis Viktorit, kes on enda vennale kulla tulnud. Emiliat ja Viktoriat seob vahemalt uks asi: mõlemal on perekonnaga muresid.

programme.title: Jõulupulm

programme.title: Saladused

programme.title: Reede ÕHTU!

programme.title: Esmakohtingud teismelistele

programme.title: Taiuslikud jõulud
programme.desc: Hingesoojendav jõululugu oma sudame kutse jargimisest isegi, kui see viib taielike ootamatusteni. Fotograaf Sophie laheb jõuludeks vanaema juurde Seattleisse. Õnnetu juhuse tõttu on Sophie sunnitud vanaema naabri last Troyd valvama. Pikapeale harjub Sophie olukorraga ning hakkab hoidmist isegi nautima. Kui Sophie ja Troy onu vahel sademed leekima loovad, peavad mõlemad raskeid valikuid langetama.

programme.title: Vahemeri
programme.desc: Kahe aasta jooksul tosinas riigis filmitud sari tutvustab meile võrdlemisi vaikese ja inimasustusega tihedalt aaristatud Vahemere loodust. Merikilpkonn ujub pika tee Prantsusmaalt Kreekasse, et jõuda munema rannale, kus ta isegi sundis. Harilikud tuunid randavad Atlandi ookeanist Vahemeres asuvatesse kudemispaikadesse ja noor kurg lendab esimest korda ule Sahara kõrbe ning Gibraltari vaina, et endale Hispaaniast kaaslane leida. Kõik need retked on tais ohtusid alates kalavõrkudest ja plastireostusest kuni tugevate tuulteni.

programme.title: Hingetõmme
programme.desc: 37-aastane kogenud arst Simon (Jeremie Renier) tootab pneumoloogia osakonnas. Arstina naeb ta iga paev surma lahedalt ja on õppinud end rankade tundmuste eest kaitsma. Kõik muutub, kui haigla naaberosakonda satub kriitilises seisundis tema ema (Marthe Keller). Simoni isiklik elu ja arstiprofessionaalsus põrkuvad ning see loob kõikuma mehe senised veendumused ja kindluse. R: David Roux.

programme.title: Lainud on jaanud
programme.desc: New Delhis sundinud režissoor Varun Trikha randas aastaid kaameraga Setomaal, et jaadvustada sealsete inimeste lugusid ning nende suhestumist mineviku ja olevikuga. Riigipiiride tõttu lõhkikistud ajalooline Petserimaa on paik, mis paneb mõtisklema kaotusest, eraldusest, lahkumissunnist ning soovist oma kultuuriga taas uhendust leida. Kuue aasta valtel tõmbab Varun Trikhat ikka ja jalle tagasi kolme kohaliku asuka juurde, kes on otsustanud jaada sellele eikellegimaale. Nad ullatavad teda lugudega oma unenagudest, mis moodunut ja poordumatult kaotatut leevendavad. Omaparasel moel aratavad need lood ules ka režissoori enda malestused ja otsingud. Ühel ool, huljatud majas peavarju leidnuna, naeb ta salaparast und oma ammulahkunud vanaisast, keda ta pole kunagi kohanud, ning ta otsustab valja selgitada, kes tema vanaisa tegelikult oli. Oma poeetilises, visuaalselt ja tahenduskihtidelt rikkas filmis paotab Varun Trikha unenaolise ukse korraga nii Eesti kui ka India uhiskonna haavadesse ning oma isiklikku perekonnalukku.

Animafilm "1895" on puhendatud filmikunsti 100. aastapaevale. Film vendade August ja Louis Lumiereide elust, mis kasitleb uldsusele seni tundmatuid fakte ning sundmusi kahe kuulsa venna, kes on lainud ajalukku kui kinematograafia leiutajad, elust. Film on illusioon. Kas illusioon on tõde? See vaide ja kusimus olid aluseks autoritele, kui nad võtsid endale õiguse kinnitada, et just nende versioon vendade Lumiereide elust ning filmikunsti sunnist on seni teadaolevatest kõige originaalsem ja ainulaadsem. Rohkete auhindadega parjatud filmi lavastasid Priit Parn ja Janno Põldma.

programme.desc: Kui panna kõrv vastu surmaagoonias vaevlevat igijaad, siis kas on võimalik mõista tema elutsuklit? Geofuusik Ludovic Moreau puuab põhjapoolusel uha kiirenevat jaa sulamist paremini mõista. Ta reisib musteeriumi lahendamiseks koos viie teadlasega Teravmagede saarestikku, kus nad paigutavad kulmunud jarvele seismilised andurid, et salvestada "jaa laulu", mis aitab ehk mõista igijaa allakaigu saladust.

Saatejuht Meelis Oidsalu vaatab koos naitleja Indrek Ojari, psuhholoog Mati Heidmetsa ja kultuuriloolase Marju Kõivupuuga filmis ohtralt kasutatud vagisõnade taha: mis neid ropendada ja kakelda armastavaid tuupe kaivitab ning mida on sel tanastegi teismeliste lemmikuks olevas filmis uldse kultuurset?

programme.desc: Katmandu buda nunnad on enesekindlad võitlejad. Võitluskunstid ei tahenda neile mitte uksnes enesekaitset, vaid peamiselt iseenda tundma õppimist. Kung fu on nende meditatsioon. Peale varvikate rituaalsete tantsude tantsimise ja palvetamise randavad nad Himaalaja maestiku uksildastes paikades, et aidata naistel end meeste kõrval maksma panna. Nad paigaldavad paikesepaneele, remondivad maju, korjavad prugi ning naitavad, kuidas kaitsta keskkonda ja kliimat.

Tema ulemaailme kuulsus on nuudseks lakanud ja saatemeeskond võtab sudameasjaks mõned tema soovid taita.

programme.desc: Mõni sõprus kestab mitu eluiga. Sudamliku uleilmse hiti "Koera elu mõtte" jarjes "Koera teekond" leiab armastatud koer Bailey oma uue saatuse ja loob murdumatu sideme, mis viib tema ja ta kallid inimesed seninagematutesse kohtadesse. Bailey (haale annab taas Josh Gad, "Lumekuninganna ja igavene talv", "Jobs") elab mõnusalt Michigani farmis oma "poisi" Ethani (Dennis Quaid, "Koera elu mõte", "Paev parast homset") ja Ethani naise Hannahga (Marg Helgenberger telesarjast "CSI: kriminalistid"). Tal on isegi uus mangukaaslane – Ethani ja Hannah pisike tutretutar CJ. Kahjuks otsustab CJ ema CJ minema viia. Kui Bailey hing valmistub sellest elust jargmisesse liikuma, lubab ta Ethanile CJ ules otsida ja teda iga hinna eest kaitsta. Nii algabki Bailey seiklus labi mitme elu, mida taidavad armastus, sõprus ja puhendumus. Tema, CJ ja CJ parim sõber Trent puutuvad kokku rõõmu ja sudame murdumisega, muusika ja naeruga, ja mõne eriti hea kõhusugamisega.

programme.desc: Ulmeline! Korvo ja Terry manipuleerivad teineteist ajas randamisega ja Yumyulack kasvatab paksu siga.

programme.title: Valgusaastate vastandid
programme.desc: Tervitused! See osa on Yumyulackist ja koaaladest!

programme.title: Kondid
programme.desc: Brennani puhtast loogikast juhindumine satub tule alla, kui ta veenab vandekohut mõrvas suudistatavat suutuks kuulutama. Kui jargnevalt tapetakse mehe parim sõber, seab Brennan meeskonnale ulesandeks leida tegelik tapja.

programme.title: Kondid
programme.desc: Koolisookla hautisest leitud inimjaanused seab Jeffersoniani meeskonnale valjakutse - lisaks mõrvari ja mõrvatu tuvastamisele tuleb neil ka tundma õppida toidutoostust ja selle karme tavasid. Angela korraldab Brennanile hiljaks jaanud vallaliste tudrukute peo, mis võtab pisut angelaliku poorde.

programme.title: Kondid
programme.desc: Booth ja Brennan uurivad võimleja mõrva, kuid tõendusmaterjali kogumist segab valgulook. Vahepeal on Brennani ja ohvri isa vaheline suhtlus Boothis muret tekitanud ja Cam tegeleb oma identiteedi vargusega.

programme.title: Kurjuse kannul
programme.desc: New Mexico kõrbest leitakse jalgadeta laip ja haiglasse tuuakse veel uks amputeeritu. Eriruhm otsib amatoorkirurgi, enne kui too jargmise ohvri ette võtab.

programme.title: Geenius ja hullumeelne
programme.desc: 19. sajandi Inglismaal tootab Oxfordi professor ajaloo esimese inglise keele sõnaraamatu kallal. Ta kasutab oma toos hullumajja lukustatud Yalei kolleegi abi.

programme.title: Saag X
programme.desc: John Kramer (Tobin Bell) on tagasi. Filmisarja "Saag" seni kõige hairivam osa raagib Jigsaw kõige isiklikumast mangust. Sundmused leiavad aset filmide "Saag" ja "Saag II" vahel, kui haige ja meeleheitel John reisib Mehhikosse riskantse ja eksperimentaalse meditsiinilise protseduuri jaoks, lootuses leida imeravim oma vahile. Ta avastab, et see kõik on pettus kõige haavatavamate inimeste tussamiseks. Kurikuulus sarimõrvar leiab uue eesmargi ja asub taas toole, poorates olukorra petturite jaoks umber. Ta teeb seda endale omasel viisil, salakavalate, hullumeelsete ja leidlike lõksude abil.

programme.title: Saatuse iroonia Ameerika moodi
programme.desc: USA 2022 romantiline komoodia Lavastaja:Marius Vaisberg Osades:Emma Roberts, Thomas Mann Margot ja Griffin usuvad mõlemad armastusse, aga pole kunagi jõudnud selle tõelise tahenduseni. Kumbki ei tea teise olemasolust, kuni uhel tormisel uusaastaool viib saatus nad kokku. Tulemuseks tõeline aparduste rada, koomiline kaos, millesse sukeldudes võivad noored saada rohkem, kui oleks arvatagi osanud.

programme.title: Zodi ja Tehu, kõrbevennad
programme.desc: See raagib loo berberipoisist, kes loob kaamliga erilise sideme, kui nad samal ajal labivad Sahara kõrbe.

programme.title: Tundekeeled. Vabatants
programme.desc: Noor lavastaja valib Broadway uude tantsulavastusse kaasaegse tantsija ja uuendusmeelse pianisti. Peagi avastavad noored end armukolmnurgast, mis kruvib pinged lakke ja kõigil tuleb halastamatus võitluses selle eest lõivu maksta.

programme.title: Tagasi tulevikku
programme.desc: Tempoka ja sudantsoojendava komoodia naol on tegemist Robert Zemeckise populaarse 1980-ndate klassikaga.

programme.title: Whiplash
programme.desc: Ambitsioonikas noor jazz-trummar Andrew Neyman õpib mainekas konservatooriumis janunedes olla parimatest parim. Terence Fletcher on pedagoog, kes on tuntud nii oma akadeemilise võimekuse kui ka kusitavalt tooreste meetodite poolest.

programme.title: X+Y
programme.desc: Puudulike sotsiaalsete oskustega teismeline imelaps matemaatikas leiab uut enesekindlust ja uusi sõprussuhteid, kui paaseb rahvusvahelisel matemaatikaolumpiaadil Briti koondisesse.

programme.title: Jeanne du Barry, kuninga favoriit
programme.desc: R: Maïwenn. Biograafiline draama. Jeanne Becu (1743-1793) sundis kehvades oludes, õmbleja abieluvalise tutrena. Sirgudes paistis ta silma oma ilu poolest ja tegi karjaari kurtisaanina. Jeannei (Maïwenn) klientideks olid aristokraadid ja õukondlased ning viimaks tutvustati teda ka kuningale. Louis XV (Johnny Depp) oli naise ilust ja intelligentsusest võlutud ning Jeanneist sai kuninga viimane ametlik armuke.

programme.title: Kass ja hiir salamissioonil
programme.desc: Kaks politseinikest eriagenti peavad lahendama salajase mineraali roovi loo. Probleemiks on see, et mõlemad on harjunud tootama eranditult oma, partneri omadest kardinaalselt erinevate meetoditega. Ja ka iseloomudelt on kangelased kui tuli ja vesi.

programme.title: Pahklivõi pistrik
programme.desc: Zak põgeneb hooldekodust, et taita oma unistus saada maadlejaks.

programme.title: Naabermaja pornostaar
programme.desc: 18-aastane Matthew Kidman on viieline õppur, kellest elu on seni otsekui mooda jooksnud. Kuni paevani, kuni ta armub naabermajja kolinud Daniellei, nailiselt suutusse iludusse. Kui poiss saab aga teada, et tema unistuste tudruk on endine pornostaar, poorab see kogu ta organiseeritud maailma pea peale.

programme.title: Lindmees ehk (võhiklikkuse ootamatu voorus)
programme.desc: Kunagine Hollywoodi superstaar Riggan Thomson, kes aastakumnete eest kuhjas kokku kuulsust ja raha filmides, kus ta kehastas kõikvõimsat superkangelast nimega Lindmees, uritab parast karidele jooksnud abielu ja karidele jooksnud karjaari taas kord rambivalgusesse naasta - sedapuhku Broadway lavalaudadel.

programme.title: Renfield
programme.desc: Kurjus ei peaks kuigi pikalt vastu ilma abilisteta. Piinatud hing Renfield (Nicholas Hoult) on lojaalseks teenriks maailma suurimale eneseimetlejale, ajaloo kurikuulsaimale vereimejale Draculale (Nicolas Cage). Mees peab varustama oma isandat saagiga, taites ka kõikvõimalikke muid ulesandeid, olgu need kuitahes alandavad. Nuud, parast sajanditepikkust orjapõlve, oleks Renfield valmis katsetama elu ilma Draculata. Esmalt on aga vaja sellest sõltuvussuhtest vabaneda...

programme.title: Kood 7500
programme.desc: Kui terroristid uritavad Berliini-Pariisi lennu ule kontrolli haarata, puuab leebe ameeriklasest kaaspiloot paasta reisijate ja meeskonna elusid, luues samal ajal ullatava sideme uhe kaaperdajaga.

programme.title: Tagasi tulevikku 2
programme.desc: Marty ja Doc lahendavad McFly perekonna probleeme 2015. aastal, kuid avastavad tagasi 1985. aastas olles uusi jamasid, mis sunnivad neid taas minema aastasse 1955, et tulevikku parandada.

programme.title: Tagasi tulevikku III
programme.desc: Filmisaaga kolmandas ja viimases osas suundub hullumeelne Doc Brown, kes leiutas ajas randava DeLoreani, aastasse 1885.

programme.title: Jurassic World
programme.desc: Kunagise Jurassic Parki asukohta ehitatakse uus lõbustuspark. Kõik laabub hasti, kuni pargi varskeim atraktsioon, geneetiliselt muundatud hiiglaslik ja hasti varjuda oskav tapamasin, põgeneb. 2015

programme.title: Kodu
programme.desc: Kui uks heidikust tulnukas, kelle nimi on Oh (Jim Parsonsi haal) Maal hadamaandub, tekib tal ootamatult sõprussuhe seiklushimulise ent kahtlustava tutarlaps Tipiga (Rihanna haal). See kummaline sõprade paar siirdub ringsõidule ule Maa, põgenedes samas Ohi tulnukatest rassikaaslaste eest. Nende meeletu reis ja uha suvenev sõprus mangib galaktikavahelistes suhetes olulist rolli.

programme.title: Džungli rutmid. Film
programme.desc: Suurt koduigatsust tundev tulnukas kukub oma kosmoselaevaga alla varvikas Aafrika džunglis. Tema uued loomadest sõbrad peavad ta oma laevale tagasi aitama ning õpetama talle sõprust ja lõbutsemist, enne kui tema kosmosevallutajast isa planeedi ule võtab.

programme.title: Kurepoeg Rihhard 2
programme.desc: Varblane Rihhard on lõplikult valmis, saamaks teejuhiks! Ta teab tapselt, kuidas talvitunud kureparvele ule Aafrika liivakõrbe, tohutute ookeanide ja ohtlike vainade koduteed naidata. Jaab ule vaid eksam sooritada – praktikandi test, et saada kureparve juhiks. See ei tohiks olla keeruline, sest Rihhard on eriline varblane, kes kasvas ules kurgedega ja on juba ammu omandanud kõik lendamise peensused. Sellest pole midagi, et ta on vaike – ta on hingelt tõeline kurg!

programme.title: Pakapikkudega kodus
programme.desc: Eestikeelne animafilm. Chloe ei ole kolimise suhtes kuigi entusiastlik, ainus laps uues kohas on tuutu naabripoiss Liam. Maja on suur ja kõle ning tais tobedaid aiapakapikke, kes arkavad akitselt ellu... Chloe saab teada, et aiapakapikud nimetavad end lihtsalt pakapikkudeks ja nende ulesandeks on kaitsta maja ja tervet planeeti veidrate konna meenutavate olendite eest. Üsna pea tulebki Chloel hakata koos pakapikkude ja isegi tuutu naabripoisi abi kasutades kaitsma oma maja ning tervet maailma! Tegelastele on oma haale kinkinud Merit Manniste, Kait Kall, Jaan Rekkor, Taavi Teplenkov, Kaisa Selde ja Liisa Pulk.

programme.title: Vaid vapratele
programme.desc: Granite Mountain Hotshots nimelise tuletõrje eliitruhma tõsielusundmustel põhinev film raagib kangelasliku loo tuletõrjujatest, kelle lootusrikkus, sihikindlus, ohvrimeelsus ja soov kaitsta enda perekondi, kogukondi ning tervet oma riiki teeb neist uhe parima tuletõrjemeeskonna USAs.

programme.title: Koera teekond
programme.desc: Mõni sõprus kestab mitu eluiga. Sudamliku uleilmse hiti "Koera elu mõtte" jarjes "Koera teekond" leiab armastatud koer Bailey oma uue saatuse ja loob murdumatu sideme, mis viib tema ja ta kallid inimesed seninagematutesse kohtadesse. Bailey (haale annab taas Josh Gad, "Lumekuninganna ja igavene talv", "Jobs") elab mõnusalt Michigani farmis oma "poisi" Ethani (Dennis Quaid, "Koera elu mõte", "Paev parast homset") ja Ethani naise Hannahga (Marg Helgenberger telesarjast "CSI: kriminalistid"). Tal on isegi uus mangukaaslane – Ethani ja Hannah pisike tutretutar CJ. Kahjuks otsustab CJ ema CJ minema viia. Kui Bailey hing valmistub sellest elust jargmisesse liikuma, lubab ta Ethanile CJ ules otsida ja teda iga hinna eest kaitsta. Nii algabki Bailey seiklus labi mitme elu, mida taidavad armastus, sõprus ja puhendumus. Tema, CJ ja CJ parim sõber Trent puutuvad kokku rõõmu ja sudame murdumisega, muusika ja naeruga, ja mõne eriti hea kõhusugamisega.

programme.title: Allikas
programme.desc: Film mehest, kes suundub milleeniumipikkusele odusseiale, et paasta oma kallim. Tema eepiline seiklus algab 16. sajandi Hispaanias, kus konkistadoor Tomas Creo alustab oma otsingut, et leida "nooruse allikas", mis kinkivat igavese elu.

programme.title: Naoga mooda asfalti
programme.desc: Mida on uks mees valmis keerulisse olukorda sattudes tegema, et kanda hoolt oma perekonna eest? Selle probleemiga põrkab uhel paeval kokku karmikaeline "vana kooli" politseinik Brett Ridgeman, kes uhes oma luhikest suutenoori omava noorema paarimehe Anthony Lurasettiga on uht jarjekordselt kahtlusalust tavaparasest veidi karmimalt kohelnud.

programme.title: Viimse verepiisani
programme.desc: Spordidraama 90ndate poksimaailma raevukamast ja koloriitsemast tegelasest Vinnie Pazienzast. Vinnie oli parast suuri raskusi lõpuks ometi tõusnud keskkaalu maailmameistriks. Kõik teed naisid tema ees valla olevat. Kuid siis sekkus mangu saatus... Pazienza sattus kohutavasse autoõnnetusse, mille tagajarjel ahvardas teda taielik halvatus. Legendaarselt jaarapaisel Pazienzal olid aga veidi teistsugused plaanid _ õppida uuesti kõndima ja tõusta uuesti maailmameistriks. Midagi vahemat ei tulnud kõne alla. Samal ajal, kui teised seda mõtet taielikuks hullumeelsuseks pidasid, alustas Vinnie oma vastupuikleva treeneri Kevin Rooney (Aaron Eckhart) abiga salajasi jõutreeninguid. Selle kõige tulemuseks oli uks uskumatumaid comebacke spordiajaloos. Film ei sobi alaealistele.

programme.title: Lepatriinu ja must kass
programme.desc: "Lepatriinu ja Must Kass. Film" raagib tavalisest Pariisi teismelisest Marinetteist, kellest saab superkangelane Lepatriinu. Maagiliste võimetega Lepatriinu peab uhendama jõud Musta Kassiga, et paasta Pariis uue kurikaela vallandatud kaose kaest.

programme.title: Hullud kapad
programme.desc: Hank on koer, kellel on ilmselt maailmas kõige vahem vedanud. Ta elab juba ammu linna kõige ohtlikumas rajoonis, satub pidevalt konfliktidesse jalkide tanavakoertega ja saab neilt pidevalt kere peale. Lisaks sellele ei võta keegi Hanki tõsiselt ja isegi sõbrad ei toeta tema suurimat unistust - saada tõeliseks võitluskunstide meistriks, samuraiks. Aga kõik poordub pea peale, kui Hank juhuslikult satub veidrasse Kakamucho linna, kus elavad ainult kassid!

programme.title: Looraks
programme.desc: Ted teeb kõik selle nimel, et leida elus puu oma unelmate tudrukule mulje avaldamiseks. Oma reisil tutvub Ted pahura ent veetleva olendi, Looraksi looga.

programme.title: Kiired ja vihased 4
programme.desc: Hitt-põnevusmarul! Kaunitar Letty tapetakse narkoparun Braga poolt. Salaagendi ametisse ennistatud Brian (Paul Walker), kes on just lõpetanud toootsa vanglas, teeb kõik, et leida pikalt jahitud narkoparun. Sama siht on ka Letty poiss-sõbral, kurikuulusal Dominic Torrettol (Vin Diesel). Lõpuks leiavad nad parima viisi kattemaksuks: uletada rooli taga kõik piirid, mis võimalik.

programme.title: Backed by the Bros
programme.desc: The Brothers must decide between an investor with a garage conversion in a historic neighbourhood, and a couple with a two-storey backyard remodel.

programme.title: Windy City Rehab
programme.desc: Windy City Rehab is a reality renovation show hosted by interior designer Alison Victoria. She and her expert team buy and restore old homes in her beloved Chicago historic neighborhoods. It is much more than a simple improvement of a house. Alison and her team are rescuing vintage houses and hold true to the original style and architecture as much as possible.

programme.title: Elu saarel
programme.desc: A couple leaves the hustle and bustle of Seattle for a home with character on Vashon Island, Washington.

programme.title: Elu saarel

programme.desc: Beachfront property dreams can come true, even on the tightest budget. These coastal home seekers discover some of the most surprisingly affordable beachfront locales, proving it doesnt take millions to live on the water.

programme.title: Uskumatu koos Dan Aykroydiga
programme.desc: Laeva- ja lennuõnnetused, kadumised ja UFO-de nagemised - mida kõike veel! Selles osas uuritakse Michigani jarve kolmnurka ja teisi metsikuid ja kummalisi kohti, sealhulgas hirmsat nukke tais saart ja koopaid, mis varjavad surmavaid viiruseid.

programme.title: Lahingud ladude parast

programme.title: AC/DC - Live in Madrid
programme.desc: No Bull documents the classic 1996 Ballbreaker tour, recorded at the Plaza De Toros De Las Ventas (Madrid, Spain). The show, involving a crane, a large model of ""Rosie"" and a finale with half a dozen blazing cannons, features 20 live tracks spanning their then 23-year career. It features 4 tracks from Ballbreaker album, as well as other classic songs by the band.

programme.title: Bastille - Reading and Leeds Festival
programme.desc: The Reading and Leeds Festivals are a pair of annual music festivals that take place in Reading and Leeds, England. The events both happen on the bank holiday weekend in August (on Friday, Saturday, Sunday), and share the same bill (occasionally with one or two exceptions). The festivals origins date to the Beaulieu Jazz Festival (1956-1961) which became the National Jazz Festival in 1961 (The National Jazz and Blues Festival in 1963) and settled in Reading in 1971. The programme is also styled to make you imagine it in the eyes of a loved one that you know.

programme.desc: Follow hosts John Walsh and his son Callahan Walsh, as they investigate and try to resolve some unsolved violent crimes and missing-child cases, relying on leads from viewers to assist authorities in catching the culprit. programme.desc: Musta huumoriga vurtsitatud (eba)romantiline komoodia. Mandy (Billie Piper, "I Hate Suzie") on oma eluga parajasse ummikusse jooksnud. Ta on kaasaegne naine. Ta on ema. Ta elab siiani ule oma vanemate keerukaid omavahelisi suhteid. Ja ta on kirjanik. Kui Mandy kohtub traditsiooniliste vaartushinnangutega Peteiga (Leo Bill, "28 paeva hiljem"), tekib nende vahel vagagi ebatraditsiooniline armusuhe…

programme.title: Suured keskvaksalid
programme.desc: Bahnhofstrasse tanava lõpus tervitavad teid aukartustaratav neorenessanslik paekivifassaad ning hoone rikkalikult kaunistatud saalid, salongid ja restoranid. Kilpkonnakilbi põhja tooni fassaadi tipus on Helvetia, Konfoderatsiooni naisallegooria. Ajalooline jaam kehastab koos oma neoklassitsistlike tornidega Šveitsi industriaalajastu õitsengut, mil toimus raudtee plahvatuslik areng. Tanapaeval peidab Zurichi HB jaam oma funktsioone hasti - marmorpõranda all peitub ulimodernne installatsioon, erinevate transpordiliikide vahelise koostoime mudel: kiirrongid, trammid, piirkondlikud kiirteed, jalgrattad... Jaam ise on transpordisõlm, milles raudteed on kolmel tasandil labi põimunud, ning mida labib iga paev pea 500 000 reisijat.

programme.title: CSI Kriminalistid

programme.title: Haneema
programme.desc: Sonja vabastatakse ja ta naaseb poegade juurde. Malestusteenistusele ilmub soovimatu kulaline. Narkoparun Pinto Rosales esitab ultimaatumi. Sonja asub Östlingi-vastases sõjas runnakule.

programme.title: Masterchef Soome
programme.desc: Võistlejad hakkavad hotelli Scandic Grand Central koogis võistkondadena omavahel mõõdu võtma. Kumma meeskonna hommikusoogikandik aratab Masterchefi kohtunikes huvi?

programme.title: Mees teab
programme.desc: Pereisa Adam on sunnitud lastega rohkem aega veetma, kui tema abikaasa Andi otsustab taas toole naasta.

programme.title: Mees teab
programme.desc: Adami klient kingib talle kaks piletit Pittsburgh Steelersi mangule ning mees seisab raske valiku ees, kas võtta endaga kaasa Andi või Don.

programme.title: Rahast tehtud koos Brian Coxiga
programme.desc: Saade vaatleb Brianit teekonnal, millel mees uurib inimeste keerukat suhet raha ja jõukusega. Saate valtel raagib mees ka omaenda lugu, alates vaesuses uleskasvamisest kuni Hollywoodi kõrgepalgaliseks naitlejaks saamiseni, kus ta kehastab uht televisiooni rikkaimat ja verejanulisimat kapitalisti. Sari on Briani missioon kõrvaldada oma hirm vaesuse ees ning lahendada raha ja õnne keeruline kusimus. Terava huumori ja kartmatu uudishimuga Brian kaarib kaised ules Bronxi supikoogis, vestleb supermodellidega Miami Beachis, kohtub kodututega Harlemis ning kulastab Londoni kõige kallimas majas uht miljardari.

programme.title: CSI Kriminalistid

programme.title: Rahu šokolaadi abil
programme.desc: Sudamlik draamakomoodia. Parast seda, kui tema perekonnale kuuluvat šokolaaditehast tabas pommirahe, puuab noor Suuria põgenik alustada uut elu Kanada vaikelinnas. Ta tahaks hakata arstiteadust õppima, ent avab isa nõudmisel siiski šokolaadiari, mis osutub vaga menukaks. Kuid noormehe hinges on siiski lõhe: kas valida omaenda kutsumus või taita muudkui isa soove. Tekkiv pinge avardab perekonna lõhki rebida… Film põhineb tõestisundinud lool.

programme.title: Parfuumid
programme.desc: Annei too on tema kirg ja kogu tema elu mõte, ta valmistab nimelt parfuume. Tal on erakordne anne - tundlik haistmismeel ja taielik puhendumus. Nagu aga sageli ikka, on liigselt toole keskendunud ja mingil alal vaga andekad loojad inimestena mitte nii kerged isiksused... Kui Anne palkab endale autojuhi, muutub tema elus palju. Lihtsast mehest, autojuht Guillaumeist saab naisele võrdne vastane, kellega koos saavad nii mõnedki elutõed selgemaks. Tegemist on sudantsoojendava linalooga sõprusest, toost ja elust.

programme.title: Karl Fredrik Österlenis
programme.desc: On aeg lukata kaima jargmine projekt - sammaskaik. Kõige keskel tekib uks mõte: akki hakkavad Karl Fredrik ja Petter Eklaholmist valja kasvama? Kuid kõigepealt korraldatakse põlluservas tootajatele pidu, mille teemaks on "Tuhat ja uks ood".

programme.title: CSI Kriminalistid

programme.title: Masterchef Soome
programme.desc: Kaheosalise pingeulesande esimeses voorus ootab võistlejaid ees Masterchefi klassika - kuubikute maitsmine. Teises voorus tuleb valmistada ebatraditsiooniline maitsete paar.

programme.title: Mees teab
programme.desc: Adamil saab tutre lasteaia õpetaja nõudmistest kullalt ning ta teeb seetõttu uhe rutaka otsuse.

programme.title: Mees teab
programme.desc: Adam hakkab Doni nõuandel enda garaažist mehekoobast tegema, kuid avastab ehmatusega, et vabanes selle kaigus võib-olla uhest Andile olulisest esemest.

programme.title: Esileedi
programme.desc: Eleanor nõuab Franklinilt julgemaid samme suure depressiooni vastu. Nixoni tagasiastumise jarel saab Bettyst esileedi vaid paar paeva enne planeeritud riigiõhtusooki. Michelle seisab Baracki ametisse nimetamise eel silmitsi mehe uleminekumeeskonna liikmete vastuseisuga.

programme.title: CSI Kriminalistid

programme.desc: Tele-esilinastus! Krimipõnevik vlogijast Stephaniest (Anna Kendrick), kes tahab teada tõde, miks ta parim sõber Emily (Blake Lively) jarsku nende vaikelinnast kadus. Stephaniele asub appi Emily abikaasa Sean (Henry Golding). Stiilne põnevik on tais poordeid ja reetmisi, saladusi ja paljastusi, armastust ja truudust, mõrva ja kattemaksu.

programme.title: Metoodiline hullumine
programme.desc: Jason Mewes asub kasutama metoodilist naitlemist, et Hollywoodis suuremat tunnustust leida, kuid hakkab aeglaselt hulluma.

programme.title: Tipptund 2
programme.desc: Mollukomoodia teises filmis peavad Hongkongi politseinik Lee ja tema jankist kolleeg Carter kinni nabima uliohtliku kurjategija. Mehed loodavad Hongkongis korralikult valja puhata, aga paraku langeb juba esimesel õhtul nende õlule ulesanne, mis viib nad Los Angelese agulitesse ja Las Vegase tuledesarasse. Kõik selleks, et tabada kurikuulus maffiaboss ja tema surmavalt kaunis kaaslanna.

programme.title: Valelikud võrgutajad
programme.desc: Hirmus, et uber A Alit piinab, poorduvad valelikud võrgutajad abi saamiseks potentsiaalse vaenlase poole.

programme.title: Apteeker Melchior
programme.desc: Tallinnas tapetakse kuulus orduruutel Clingenstein - kangelane, kes vabastas Laanemere piraatidest. Nuud on ta pea maha raiutud ja suu munte tais topitud. Kadunud on kuldkett, mille ta alles samal paeval ostis. Kohtuharra Wenzel Dorn võtab mõrvapaigale kaasa noore apteekri Melchior Wakenstede. Noormees on nagu verekoer, kes oskavat ka surnutega raakida. Melchiori nutikus ja Dorni oskamatus viivad aga selleni, et kogu mõrvaloo lahendamine jaab apteekri õlule. Peagi selgub, et tapetud ruutel tuli Tallinnasse eriulesandega. Kõik jaljed viivad dominiiklaste kloostrisse. Sealt algab mõrvade rida, kus ohvriks kõik, kes puutunud kokku salaparase "Tallinna vangiga". Apteeker Melchiori triloogia põhineb raamatumuugi edetabelite tipust tuntud romaanisarjal. Stsenaristid Indrek Hargla, Elmo Nuganen ja Olle Mirme põimisid esimeses filmis raamatust "Apteeker Melchior ja Oleviste mõistatus" tuntud tegelased ja sundmused taiesti uute, filmi jaoks loodud keerdkaikudega.

programme.title: Öokulaline
programme.desc: Eesti uks rikkamaid inimesi, Hansapanga ja LHV panga asutaja Rain Lõhmus elab juba enam kui 10 aastat Šveitsis, maalilise Lugano jarve kaldal. Saatejuht Mart Normet uurib, kas raha teeb õnnelikuks ja miks ikkagi Eestis hinnad nii kallid on? Lisaks LHV panga nõukogu juhtimisele panustab Rain Lõhmus suure osa oma energiast poja kasvatamisele ja tema tennisetreeningutesse. Miks on neil aga kodus robotkoer ja millist imelikku hommikusooki Lõhmuste juures pakutakse, seda ja palju muud saate kuulda ja naha tanases seikluslikus saates. Režissoor Andreas Lenk, operaator Madis Reimund, helioperaator Tanel Paats, toimetajad Sigrid Salutee ja Kairit Tsaro.

programme.title: Kodus ja võõrsil
programme.desc: Bronte skeemitamine tasub end ara. Kas Mackenzie õpib Levit usaldama? Edeni viha ei lahtu.

programme.title: Monk
programme.desc: Kui naine sõidab teelt valja ja sureb, leitakse tema keha salaparaselt kolm hommikut hiljem selgeltnagija poolt, kes on tuntud tõe vaanamise poolest. Monk peab avastama, kas ta raagib seekord tõtt või vastasel juhu laskma mõrvaril vabadusse jaada.

programme.title: Magipaastjad
programme.desc: Emili kavatseb oma surnud mehe leinamisega rahu teha ja laheb koos Tobiasega magimatkale. Juhtub õnnetus. Andreas leiab markmed, millest selgub matkajate asukoht. Magipaastjad asuvad paasteoperatsioonile, mis kujuneb katastoofiliseks. Algab võitlus elu ja surma peale.

programme.title: Saatuslik kiri
programme.desc: Vaid mõned minutid enne laulatust tekitab Hatice kaik Asli ja Mehmeti vahel konflikti. Hatice on pettunud, et Alanur end laulatusel ei ilmuta ega skandaali tekita. Mehmet pole arvestanud, et tal tuleb aega veeta ka Asli sõpradega. Alanur joob end tais ja rikub Asli ja Mehmeti pulmaoo.

programme.title: Lena Lorenz
programme.desc: Floral on kaval mõte, kuidas oma pettusest puhtalt valja tulla, ta raagib sellest Lenale ja palub abi. Lena soovitab Markole kõik ules tunnistada. Eval on Vinzi bussifirma suhtes oma salaplaan. Julia poeg Tim ja ta pruut Celine jõuavad kohale, Julia ullatuseks on Celine rase. Julia ja Celine vahel ei teki kohe sooje tundeid.

programme.title: Naabriplika
programme.desc: Ühel ilusal paeval halvab Esna argielu filmipalavik. Kui nuud kõik ausalt ara raakida, siis saab kogu jama alguse sellest, et vallavanema naine vaatab õhtul filmi. Või siis hoopis sellest, et Sookratesel kits saab uhelt moodasõitvalt autolt loogi. Ja kuna autojuhil raha ei juhtu olema, pakub ta Sookratesele kompensatsiooniks filmikaamerat. Igatahes on vallavanemal selge nagemus, et uude ja ennenagamtult kõrgkunstilisse filmi kõlbab esinema Robert De Niro. Kahjuks jaab Robertil siiski objektiivsetel põhjustel Esna uues kinofilmis osalemine ara. Kuid see ei peata Paavlit. Kunst ei upu. Loomulikult tungleb filmi umber ka palju tuutuid mittekunstilisi tegelasi. Aga kull Paavel juba teab.Labi raskuste luuakse maailma filmikunsti uus ja seninagematu meistritoo. Samal ajal kuulab Varik vallavanema korraldusel ule Maivit. Tuleb tunnistada, et ka see pole sugugi kerge too.

programme.desc: Marek tuleb Kristiina juurde ning uritab diskreetselt valja uurida, kas tudrukutel on taid. Sassu vihastab isa peale, sest ei taha, et vanaema ara laheks. Emma leiab Rasmuse uksinda kodust ning vallandab momentaalselt uue lapsehoidja.

programme.title: Apteeker Melchior. Timuka tutar
programme.desc: Keskaegse krimipõneviku kolmandas filmis juhtub Melchiori naine Keterlyn jõhkra kallaletungi tunnistajaks. Tundmatu noormehe elu õnnestub paasta, kuid malu kaotanud ohver ei tea, kes ta on ja kuidas enda jaoks võõrasse Tallinnasse sattus. Sundmuskohalt leitud sõrmus juhatab Melchiori oise vennaskonna jalile, kusimusi tekitab ka laadapaeval esinenud veiderdajate trupp. Hirmuaratavad margid vihjavad, et ohus pole uksnes tapmiskatsest toibuv tundmatu, vaid ka teda ravivad Melchior ja Keterlyn.

programme.title: Tipptund 3
programme.desc: Marulikomoodia. Uurija Carter (Chris Tucker) ja inspektor Lee (Jackie Chan) tegutsevad jalle, sedapuhku aga Pariisis. Meeste missiooniks on nurjata ulemaailmne kuritegelik vandenõu ja paasta vana sõbra elu. Asja segavateks faktoriteks on aga nimelt tõsiasjad, et mehed ei oska ei kohalikku keelt, ei tunne linna ja veel vahem on neil aimu pariislaste igapaevakommetest.

programme.title: Valelikud võrgutajad
programme.desc: Valelikud on valmis Ali paastmise nimel ukskõik mida tegema. Saatuslik viga aga muudab kogu olukorda.

programme.title: Apteeker Melchior. Viirastus
programme.desc: Keskaegse krimipõneviku teises filmis ehmatab oovahti kohutav viirastus - rikka kaupmehe traagiliselt uppunud tutar. Hommikuks on vahimees kõrgest tornist surnuks kukkunud ja kahtlastes õnnetustes kaotavad elu veel mitu inimest. Neid sundmusi uuriva Melchiori teed ristuvad nii lõbutudruku kui preestriga, nii võõramaa kunstniku kui hullunud ketseriga. Vihjed viivad ta Pirita kloostrisse, mille sunged võlvid varjavad unustusse maetud ohtlikku saladust. Samal ajal vaevab Melchiorit mõistatus, miks ta armastatu Keterlyn uhtakki nende kihluse katkestab…

programme.desc: Marek tuleb Kristiina juurde ning uritab diskreetselt valja uurida, kas tudrukutel on taid. Sassu vihastab isa peale, sest ei taha, et vanaema ara laheks. Emma leiab Rasmuse uksinda kodust ning vallandab momentaalselt uue lapsehoidja.

programme.title: Kodus ja võõrsil
programme.desc: Cash puuab Edenit ja Felicityt lepitada. Dana on kahtlustav. Irene pakub valja šokeeriva lahenduse.

programme.title: Monk
programme.desc: Kohtunik mõrvatakse 911 kõnet tehes, kuid enne surma nimetab ta oma rundaja, kurikuulsa kurjategija Dale Biederbecki nime. Probleem on aga selles, et Dale "Vaal" kaalub ule 360 kilo ja pole aastaid oma voodist lahkunud.

programme.title: Magipaastjad
programme.desc: Helikopter kukub alla ja Mihael murrab jalaluu. Ilm halveneb ja paastjatest pole jalgegi. Andrease ja Tobiase isa uritavad kadunud poegi ules leida. Nii Tobiase kui Mihaeli seisund halveneb. Kas mehed õnnestub veel õigeaegselt paasta?

programme.title: Saatuslik kiri
programme.desc: Vihane Alanur haavab Bestet tema jaoks kõige tundlikumal teemal. Asli naeb esimest korda Seheri tegelikku palet ja saab aimu, mis ootused ammal talle on. Nevzat tuletab Seherile meelde, kui palju ta talle minevikus abiks on olnud. Alanur otsustab korraldada Mehmeti ja Asli auks enda pool peo, kuid enne tuleb tal minna Ziya pere juurde vabandust paluma.

programme.title: Lena Lorenz
programme.desc: Romy ja Ben ootavad rõõmuga esimest last, neil on plaanis peale sunnitust Rosenheimi kolida. Romy isa aga laheb seda kuuldes endast valja, tema tulid Beniga lahevad veel agedamaks ja viivad traagilise lõpuni. Eva alustas tood bussijuhina, Aimee on leidnud unistuste maja. Celine tootab Lena juures ja saab vaga hasti hakkama, sama ei saa oelda tema ja Julia suhete kohta.

programme.title: Naabriplika
programme.desc: Vallavanem on hadas odavate hiina asjadega. Esna valla huvides otsustab Paavel Hiinale sõja kuulutada. Kull pole see sugugi meeltmooda Kaitseministeeriumile. Kuid Paavel põnnama ei loo. Kibekiirelt luuakse Esnasse oma isiklik Hiinavastane ministeerum ja kui Sookrates metsast kahtlase eseme leiab, võib Paavel oma strateegiat planeerima hakata. Tola satub Aliina juurde lõõre puhastama. Suures lõõripuhastamise tuhinas kukub Tola aga katuselt ja saab sellise obaduse, mida oleks raske kirjeldada isegi kirjanikul. Igal juhul muudab see obadus nii mõndagi Esna igapaevaelus. Kerepa, kes uues vastloodud ministeeriumis tood ei saa, loob endale samuti ministeeriumi. Aga nagu alati, pole Kerepa ettevõtmistel seda sara ja hoogu. Kirikõpetaja langeb aga jarjest sugavamale Kroosmani investeerimisplaani.

programme.title: Reporter
programme.desc: Uudistemagasinide lipulaev, mis toob olulisemad ja põnevamad uudised kodumaalt ja mujalt maailmast vaatajateni Reporterile omasel mahlakal moel. Saatejuhid on alati soliidsed Jaanus Koort, Simon Suviste ja Tõnis Sarap.

programme.title: 15 kusimust
programme.desc: Kodumaine strateegiline malumang, mille muudab kaasahaaravaks põnev vihjete susteem ja strateegia element. Saates on vastamisi kaks mangijat, kel on võimalus hakata panustama enda tugevustele ning samal ajal vastase nõrkusele. Mõnikord võib selline tegutsemine edu tuua, aga teinekord hoopis katte maksta ning vajalikest punktidest ilma jatta. Saadet juhib Juri Butšakov.

programme.title: Kolm naist karavanis. Prantsusmaa
programme.desc: Kristel Aaslaid, Eeva Esse-Sõõrumaa ja Carola Madis on seekord võtnud karavaniga suuna Prantsusmaa poole. Kuigi reis Tallinnast algab suure hurraaga ja shampanja klaase kokku luues, ootab juba maandudes ees korralik kaos. Juba esimese 24 tunniga kaob turvatunne, suunataju ja palju narvirakke.

programme.title: Jahihooaeg
programme.desc: 45-aastane Eva (Harriet Toompere) on hiljuti lahutanud ja kardab nuud kaotada nii oma poja kui ka sõbranna eksmehe uuele noorele, edukale ja saravale armsamale Isabelile (Grete Kuld). Et oma positsioonid tagasi võita, laheb Eva koos sõbranna Marleeni (Mirtel Pohla) ja oma uue sarava rivaali Isabeliga road-tripile, mis viib naised kokku erinevate meestega, ulikoomiliste apardustega, veelgi koomilisemate tulidega, paris tõelise jahipidamisega ja eelkõige iseendaga, et keset jõulusaginat mõista, mis on ikkagi elus kõige olulisem. Uues kodumaises komoodias astuvad peategelaste kõrval ules Jan Uuspõld, Priit Loog, Kaire Vilgats, Koit Toome, Hendrik Sal-Saller, Haide Mannamae, Tõnu Oja, Indrek Taalmaa, Raimo Pass, Anne Paluver jpt.

programme.title: Apteeker Melchior
programme.desc: 2020. suve hakul algasid Eesti kõige suurejoonelisema filmitriloogia võtted, kus sattusid kokku esimene laastav koroonaviiruse laine, produktsioonilt ulikeerukas projekt ning aarmiselt tihe tootmisgraafik. Saade viib vaataja Apteeker Melchiori filmi telgitagustesse, toob valja põnevad intervjuud ning seninagemata kaadrid ainulaadsest filmitootmisest, mille kaigus valmis korraga mitte uks või kaks, vaid koguni kolm taispikka mangufilmi.

programme.title: ABBA
programme.desc: Film heidab pilgu parimate ABBA kaverite telgitagustesse ja selgitab valja, miks maailmakuulsad artistid on ikka ja jalle otsustanud luua oma versioone ABBA igihaljastest hittidest.

programme.title: Valelikud võrgutajad
programme.desc: Valelikud võrgutajad puuavad peita oma viga, kuid sellest kannatavad nende romantilised suhted.

programme.title: Apteeker Melchior. Timuka tutar
programme.desc: Keskaegse krimipõneviku kolmandas filmis juhtub Melchiori naine Keterlyn jõhkra kallaletungi tunnistajaks. Tundmatu noormehe elu õnnestub paasta, kuid malu kaotanud ohver ei tea, kes ta on ja kuidas enda jaoks võõrasse Tallinnasse sattus. Sundmuskohalt leitud sõrmus juhatab Melchiori oise vennaskonna jalile, kusimusi tekitab ka laadapaeval esinenud veiderdajate trupp. Hirmuaratavad margid vihjavad, et ohus pole uksnes tapmiskatsest toibuv tundmatu, vaid ka teda ravivad Melchior ja Keterlyn.
